Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.74,0:01:44.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:102749,104334}Mikako! Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.45,0:01:45.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:104459,105501}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.62,0:01:47.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:105627,107503}– Good morning!\N– Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:54.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:110715,114302}Meimi, you look\Nvery sleepy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.42,0:01:56.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:114427,116179}Yeah, yesterday's homework…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:01:57.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116304,117263}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.09,0:02:00.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:118097,120141}Why are you looking\Nso gloomy in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:01.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:120224,121643}What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.72,0:02:05.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:121726,125021}With that expression on your face,\Nyou can't enjoy the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:07.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:126147,127190}Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.98,0:02:09.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:127982,129817}You two are so close!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:12.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:129942,132111}Mikako! What are\Nyou talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:16.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:134030,136366}You're running\Nthis early, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.94,0:02:19.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:136949,139535}Because soon we'll\Ncommemorate the year…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.66,0:02:22.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:139661,142246}…of the Olympics,\Nand we're going to have…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.33,0:02:23.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:142330,143831}…the Seika Open Marathon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.91,0:02:25.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:143915,145458}That's right! See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.21,0:02:29.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:147210,149295}Saruwatari was pretty excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:32.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149420,152090}He says that Mikako\Nwill represent our school…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.21,0:02:34.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152215,154175}…and she's favored\Nto win the race.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.59,0:02:37.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154592,157553}I see… Mikako!\NGood luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:40.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159097,160098}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:46.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:161766,166062}STEAL A WOMAN'S\NMARATHON RUNNING SHOES
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:49.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:167605,169565}Hey, Meimi! After school today…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.64,0:02:51.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:169649,171192}…can you go shopping with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:52.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:171484,172485}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.06,0:02:54.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:173069,174696}Hi, Haneoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:57.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174946,177824}I want you to go\Nsomewhere with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:03:01.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:178282,181411}Sorry! I've just made plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:05.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:182537,185665}Well, it has to be today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:08.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:186332,188793}To tell you the truth,\NI'm writing an article…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:11.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188918,191295}…about an attractive runner's\Nroad to victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:12.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191879,192964}I know! It's a special…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:14.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193089,194841}…about the senior, Mikako Tamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:17.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:195508,197093}What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:20.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198261,200805}Today Mikako will practice\Non the riverbank.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:23.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:201347,203224}I want to take some pictures there…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:25.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:203349,205059}…showing her supportive friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:27.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:205852,207895}I was wondering if you would be\None of her fans in the photographs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.81,0:03:31.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:208813,211190}Sounds like fun!\NLet's all go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:32.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211524,212859}You told us your plan…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:35.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:212942,215194}…but your real purpose\Nis to take pictures…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:36.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:215319,216612}…of Meimi, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:38.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:216738,218406}Well, that's one of the reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.74,0:03:39.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218740,219991}In the past week…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:42.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220116,222452}…I've been following her\Nin order to write an article about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:44.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:222910,224662}But she doesn't look very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:47.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:224912,227749}So I was wondering\Nif we could all try to cheer her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:50.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:228458,230460}Good for you, Sawatari!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:53.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231127,233379}All right! I'm going\Nto be supportive of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:55.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233671,235131}Yeah! That's a good angle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:57.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:235465,237216}Haneoka is in the middle!\NYeah! That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.34,0:03:58.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:237341,238301}Very good!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:03.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241053,243473}There she is! Mikako!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:05.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243556,245057}– Yay!\N– Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:16.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:254942,256694}Oh, all of you came!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:17.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:256778,257779}Take this…!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:19.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257945,259071}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:20.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:259155,260740}We're going to speed it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:21.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:260823,261949}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:38.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:277632,278674}Mr. Tsukamoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:40.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:278800,280051}Remember my shoes\Nthat you had the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:41.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:280176,281719}What did you do with them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.59,0:04:45.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283596,285473}Go away!\NWe're in the middle of a workout!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:49.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287433,289018}Mikako!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:51.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:290019,291145}Come on, Hiroko! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:52.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291270,292355}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:57.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294649,297735}I did it!\NI captured their rivalry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:00.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298569,300154}Was I wrong…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:01.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:300530,301531}Yeah…!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.74,0:05:08.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:306744,308204}Who's that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:12.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:308871,312750}She is considered\Nthe biggest threat to Mikako.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:15.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:313042,315461}She's Hiroko Hashimoto\Nfrom Seika Minami Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.92,0:05:17.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:315920,317755}She doesn't seem very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:20.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:318339,320299}She's the daughter\Nof the Chairman of the Board.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:22.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:320466,322260}She has her own coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:25.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:323094,325721}Oh, is that the man on the bicycle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:32.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331602,332687}I wonder if something's…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:34.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:332812,334146}…going on between those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:44.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342113,344574}Don't you need to practice today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:47.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:345741,347076}I don't care about practice…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:51.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:347618,351205}I… I can't run anymore…!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:55.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351831,355459}If you don't mind,\Ncould you tell me why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:05:59.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:358045,359255}The other day…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:02.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359422,362675}…we had a practice workout\Nat Seika Minami Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:04.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:363342,364677}Hiroko's coach…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.84,0:06:06.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364844,366304}…Mr. Tsukamoto approached me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:09.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:366637,369140}Mikako. As usual,\Nyour times are great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:10.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:369515,370641}Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:12.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:371183,372226}I would like to see…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:13.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:372435,373603}…your custom jogging shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:16.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373769,376397}We'd like to check them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:18.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:377148,378316}Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:22.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:380359,382904}He said he would\Nreturn them right away…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:26.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383029,386365}…and I lent them to him\Nwithout being suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:32.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389493,392872}The next day, the shoes\Nwere returned right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:34.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393122,394540}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:36.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395041,396459}Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:41.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399545,401297}The shoes he returned\Nweren't mine…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:44.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401589,404133}…and a pin was hidden inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:46.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404467,406177}If I had been wearing\Nthem in the race…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:47.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406302,407929}…and didn't notice,\Nmy foot would have been…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.18,0:06:52.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410181,412558}That's very cruel sabotage!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:58.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:413184,418189}My shoes were custom-made\Nabroad for my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:00.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418981,420232}If I order another pair…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.44,0:07:02.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:420441,422193}…they won't be here\Nin time for the race…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:05.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422526,425780}Without them my times\Nwon't be good enough to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:10.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426322,430076}My real shoes must be\Nat Tsukamoto's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:12.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:430451,432662}I went there to get them back…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.82,0:07:14.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:432828,434413}…but they chased me away…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:23.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:439210,443047}Don't worry. I'm sure\NGod will protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:34.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452306,454934}All right, Hiroko!\NThat's all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:38.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457520,458896}Thank you for the workout!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:47.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:466445,467405}Father…!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:55.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:473452,475037}Tsukamoto, you're positive…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:57.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475162,477540}…that you can assure\Nmy Hiroko of a win, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:07:59.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478332,479458}Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:01.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:479667,481085}When she gets first place…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:04.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481293,484672}…you'll keep your promise,\Nwon't you, Mr. Chairman?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:06.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:485297,486507}I'm aware of what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.04,0:08:09.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:487049,489301}If you've trained a runner\Nwho took first place…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.38,0:08:11.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:489385,491220}…it's easier for me to reward you…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.30,0:08:13.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:491303,493389}…with a winning bonus\Nand a promotion…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:15.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:493514,495182}…to the school's Head Coach…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:16.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:495266,496392}…at the board meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:19.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:497018,499103}I'll ensure that she wins\Nno matter what…!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:21.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:499562,501480}I have a secret plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:22.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501731,502982}I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.14,0:08:24.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:503149,504942}If my daughter\Nbecomes the top runner…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:27.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:505067,507153}…my position at the school\Nwill be solidified.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:30.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507903,510614}Coach! In exchange\Nfor my winning…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:32.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510823,512783}…he'll receive money\Nfrom my father…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:41.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518622,521208}Mikako's shoes were switched?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:43.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:522168,523210}It's as I suspected…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.91,0:08:45.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523919,525504}Did you know about it, Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:47.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:526088,527131}Well, yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:49.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527631,529842}Then can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:51.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:530009,531302}Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:54.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531719,534180}St. Tail won't allow\Ncheaters to tarnish…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:55.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:534305,535931}…the sanctity of sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:58.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:536307,538267}But we don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:01.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538768,541395}The race will start\Nat 10:00 a.m. tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:02.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:541896,542938}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:06.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543397,546317}I should get Mikako's\Nshoes back tonight then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:07.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546400,547401}You can count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.65,0:09:17.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:555659,557536}It's tomorrow at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:21.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559038,561582}Asuka, are you going\Nto watch the race?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:24.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:561874,564168}The race is\Nbeing held during class.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:26.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564293,566128}But Sawatari was telling us…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:27.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:566253,567963}…he'd get permission\Nto go take pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:29.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:568172,569799}He is special…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.00,0:09:31.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:570007,571467}…because he's\Nwith the school newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:34.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:571884,574095}Then we should\Nget permission, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:36.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:574220,576639}I'm Mikako's fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:38.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:576806,578599}Just because you're her fan…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:41.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:578682,581560}…doesn't mean Sister is going\Nto give you automatic permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.89,0:09:43.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:581894,583187}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:44.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583270,584271}You think so…?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.89,0:09:47.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:586899,587858}"Tonight…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:49.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:587983,589693}…I'm going to Seika Minami Academy,\Nin the track team's room…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.77,0:09:51.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:589777,591612}…to get a pair of jogging shoes."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.23,0:09:53.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:592238,593948}It's St. Tail's warning note!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:56.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594073,596283}I have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:57.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596408,597409}Hey, Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:02.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:600496,602331}I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:04.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603040,604375}Welcome home, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:06.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605042,606085}Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.21,0:10:07.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:606210,607169}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:08.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:607378,608462}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:09.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:608671,609672}Here! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:11.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:610214,611799}What? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:13.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:612091,613467}Over here, Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.97,0:10:19.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616971,619056}Oh. It's no use hiding…!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.93,0:10:21.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:619932,621517}Aha! I've got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:23.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:622017,623185}Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.56,0:10:24.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:623561,624895}Success! Success!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:26.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624979,626438}Boy, where's Mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:28.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627022,628816}Here I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:31.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628983,631193}Mom! Were you there all along?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:32.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:631318,632278}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.40,0:10:33.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632403,633779}Then the shadow\Nin the kitchen was…?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:37.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:634196,637283}Here it is! It's my idea\Nfor some new magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.74,0:10:38.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:637741,638951}Using a mirror and a light…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:41.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:639034,641495}… I can make an item,\Nwhich isn't there, appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:44.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:641996,644206}Wow! That's great, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.87,0:10:46.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644874,646917}Let me have\Nthat trick for a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:50.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:647334,650045}Meimi! Why don't you\Ncome down and have a snack?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:51.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:650462,651589}Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:53.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:651881,653299}Meimi may…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.54,0:10:56.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:653549,656927}…seriously be thinking\Nabout following in my footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:10:58.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:657219,658304}I wonder…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:04.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:662683,664894}Now let's get to work!
Comment: 0,0:11:09.69,0:11:09.69,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:669690,669690}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:14.69,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:674695,674695}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:19.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:678157,679408}BASEBALL CLUB
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:21.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:679533,681035}TRACK AND FIELD CLUB
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:34.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693172,694173}First place…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:39.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696592,699386}Could these be?!\NMikako Tamura's shoes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.64,0:11:49.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:707645,709480}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.18,0:11:53.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:710189,713025}Coach! These are\NMikako Tamura's shoes, aren't they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:54.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:713275,714735}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:56.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714944,716862}Why were these in our\Nlocker room?! Please explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:00.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:718656,720783}These are…\NHiroko, they're for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:03.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:721200,723118}For me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:06.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723410,726372}It may not be appropriate\Nfor me to say this…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.83,0:12:07.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:726830,727790}…but to be honest with you…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:10.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:727873,730751}…your current times aren't\Ngood enough to beat Mikako.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:11.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:730876,731835}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.04,0:12:14.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:732044,734046}I've done it because\NI've been thinking about you…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:16.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734171,736006}…trying so hard to measure up…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.09,0:12:17.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736090,737591}…to the expectations of the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:20.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:738926,740344}It's not fair…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:21.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:740469,741637}…to take her shoes…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:23.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:741762,743514}…and her chance of recording\Na winning time! Coach!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:26.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:744265,746976}I'm going to return\Nthe shoes to Mikako!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:28.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:747101,748060}Wait, Hiroko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:33.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:752106,753065}That's…!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:34.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:753524,754483}Stop it! Hiroko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:35.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:754858,755859}It's bitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:38.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:756193,758529}Coach! This isn't\NMikako's special drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:40.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:758696,760030}You did something to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.99,0:12:42.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:760990,762741}That's what I'm telling you…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:45.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:763534,765411}…I want you to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:47.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765786,767746}How dare you…!\NI know that…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:50.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:768414,770249}…my winning will make you money!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.41,0:12:52.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:771417,772918}You talked my father into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:54.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:773043,774044}How dare you…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:56.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:774169,776463}…make me your cash cow?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:12:58.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:776714,778549}I won't run tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:13:00.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:778632,780634}I don't want to run\Nif I have to cheat my opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.35,0:13:12.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:790352,792688}Mr. Tsukamoto, Hiroko!\NIs something wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:15.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:794106,795107}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:17.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:795232,797192}We're just getting nervous\Nbecause the race is close.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:19.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:797943,799445}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:22.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:799903,802823}Asuka Jr. and the police are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:24.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:803198,804658}Just a moment.\NI'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.78,0:13:25.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:804783,805743}The police…?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:28.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806577,808287}Keep these shoes in the locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.95,0:13:30.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:808954,810706}No one's going to get\Nsuspicious seeing shoes…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:31.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810831,811957}…in the track team's locker room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:33.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812082,813042}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:35.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:814585,815961}Don't do anything stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:37.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:816503,817838}I'll take care of the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:40.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:818339,820924}You should think only of running.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:45.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:824720,825679}A warning note?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.13,0:13:47.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:826138,827806}Mysterious thief or whatever…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:49.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:828098,829183}How can you investigate…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:51.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:829266,831185}…every little tip?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:54.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:831435,834980}But St. Tail doesn't steal\Nwithout a good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.64,0:13:56.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:835647,836732}The fact that it's\Njust before the race…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.85,0:13:57.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:836857,837941}…makes me think\Nof something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:13:59.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:838734,839693}Among your athletes…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.81,0:14:01.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:839818,841445}…is there anyone\Nwho could be her target?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:04.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:842029,844615}We have an important\Nrace tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.15,0:14:07.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845157,847534}I don't want you to make it\Na big deal, if possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:11.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:848243,851580}We won't bother anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.03,0:14:13.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:852039,853707}Then suit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.37,0:14:20.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:857378,860672}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:27.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:866053,867012}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:30.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:869556,870599}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:35.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:872810,875646}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:51.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:889034,891036}Mikako's special shoes have…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:53.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891245,893330}…the initial "M."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:54.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:893705,894915}Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.74,0:14:56.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895749,896708}Count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:02.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898877,902089}May the blessings\Nof God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:14.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:913892,914852}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:18.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:916019,918397}Hiroko! You're still here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:20.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:919356,920858}You'd better go home and rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:22.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:920941,922276}Otherwise, you can't\Nrun well tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:25.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:922901,925612}Coach, I'd like to stay with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:27.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:926071,927114}Is she…?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:29.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:927281,929783}She's the ace of our team,\NHiroko Hashimoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.54,0:15:38.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:937541,938625}What…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:41.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:939168,941128}Mr. Tsukamoto and Hiroko.\NGet out of the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:42.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941253,942337}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.84,0:15:46.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944840,946049}It's St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.09,0:15:48.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:947092,948051}Catch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:52.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:950554,952055}– She's outside! Chase her!\N– Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:03.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:960814,963317}Well, where are the shoes…?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:08.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:967404,968822}These must be them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.36,0:16:12.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:971366,972451}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:14.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972618,974369}She hasn't stolen anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:22.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:980083,982252}This must be a dummy!\NThe locker room is at risk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:24.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:982961,984004}Darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:29.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987508,989510}St. Tail! Come down!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:31.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989635,991512}Come down and give me a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:43.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002856,1003899}It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.69,0:16:48.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005692,1008862}…Show…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:51.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009279,1011073}…Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.54,0:17:01.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1020541,1021875}All right! I'm coming up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.41,0:17:05.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024419,1025796}What…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.87,0:17:07.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025879,1027422}Hiroko! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:13.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031927,1033845}Hiroko! Come down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:17.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034221,1037432}If you can't race tomorrow,\Nmy job is…!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.97,0:17:19.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1037975,1039142}That's what I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.60,0:17:20.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039601,1040727}What did she say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:24.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1041395,1044606}St. Tail!\NWhy don't you attack me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:27.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045607,1047401}She's trying to provoke me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:30.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048443,1050028}Asuka Jr., I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:31.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050487,1051822}PIease stop Hiroko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:33.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051989,1053657}Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:35.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1053907,1055826}And I'll catch St. Tail, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.45,0:17:46.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064459,1066545}Stay still up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:50.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066962,1070132}Don't come any closer.\NIt's better if I get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:53.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1070591,1073135}What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.59,0:17:56.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073594,1076221}If I get hurt and can't race…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:58.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076305,1078557}…you and my father\Nwill think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:00.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078807,1080892}Come down, Hiroko!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:03.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081977,1083562}Don't come any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:16.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094948,1096408}Mr. Tsukamoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:19.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097534,1099661}I'm taking Mikako's shoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:22.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100329,1102372}You'd better not interfere anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.83,0:18:25.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1103832,1105292}Mikako's shoes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:27.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105375,1107669}What's going on, Mr. Tsukamoto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.87,0:18:29.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107878,1109546}What's the explanation here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:32.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1110964,1112507}It's all over…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.46,0:18:35.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1113467,1115093}That's good…\NThis is the way…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:41.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1119556,1121850}TAMURA
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:46.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125520,1126605}These are…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.60,0:18:52.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1130609,1132903}Thank you, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:06.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1145165,1146166}Mikako!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:07.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1146583,1147709}Hiroko!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.16,0:19:09.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1148168,1149920}It's time to compete, Mikako!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:12.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150462,1152839}Yes. I won't be easy on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.21,0:19:15.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1154216,1155717}On your mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:17.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156468,1157636}Get set!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.89,0:19:30.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167896,1170816}Mikako was very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:34.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171233,1174277}The coach confessed to everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.48,0:19:37.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174486,1177239}So Hiroko can also race\Nwithout any problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:38.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1177447,1178448}Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.57,0:19:41.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1178573,1181451}Then the result of the race\Nis even more exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.36,0:19:45.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182369,1185372}Hey! Sister gave us\Nspecial permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:47.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1185747,1187082}So we can go now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:49.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187249,1189334}– Yeah!\N– We'll be in time for the finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:55.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193964,1195924}Hurry up! Here! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:29.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1225954,1229416}SEIKA CITY MARATHON
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:36.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234504,1236256}Tied for first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:38.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236381,1238175}This is the first time\Nin the history of the race!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:40.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1238300,1240302}Great! Both of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.38,0:20:44.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1240385,1244347}Yeah. I guess\NSt. Tail and I are rivals, too.
